QuestData.Title: In Plain Sight
QuestData.Description:
That sound! It came from the direction of the obelisk at Provis Flora.
Impossible. We've let no one through. Hurry, $n. Follow me!
QuestData.LogDescription: Defend the obelisk at Provis Flora.
QuestData.RewardText: They managed to hide themselves. This bodes poorly for us.
